  {cat:"Agentic AI",q:"Which of these is NOT a typical tool available to an AI agent?",opts:["Web search","Code execution","Generating random human DNA","Database query (Text-to-SQL)"],ans:2,exp:"Agents can use web search, code execution, SQL, APIs — but generating human DNA is not a software tool category."},
